ities.com/garaigh/buddy2.txt height=127 width=107></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: HEX!! (my new story!)</span><hr size=1> i think you mean they want to start a revolution not a war. (there is a difference.) <br>
<br>
ever read the Wheel of Time books by Robert Jordan? he had a race of humans that used magical chains on those who worked magic. they were then controlled by others and &quot;trained&quot; do work their magic on command. the tricky part was that every assumed that all of those who worked magic were evil/unstable. it turned out that in order to work the chains the person in charge had to be able to work magic as well. thus, upper class people were allowed to be in control, while those who were lower class ended up being slaves. <br>
<br>
i think you might try working something like that in. it's interesting to have the &quot;hexers&quot; in control. but i don't think it's quite enough. maybe try adding another dimension to it. perhaps you have to go to school in order to be able to practice hexes. only it's expensive so only the rich can afford it. those who aren't certified (i.e. those who have been to school) are punished if they work hexes. <br>
<br>
just my two cents. in future maybe you could spell check your posts. it's hard to read things that are full of typos. (there is a spellcheck button at the bottom of the posting form.) <br>
<br>
